rows.label: tlk70000023_02_msg0002
rows.name:
In Acedia, they say the Holy Grail is divine
revelation, but he looks more like a
monster to me!

rows.label: tlk70000023_02_msg0003
rows.name:
If only that brave knight were here
now... Ornella-sama...

rows.label: tlk70000023_02_msg0004
rows.name:
Years ago, back when I was just a girl,
there were stories of a great knight in
a place called Hyber Village.

rows.label: tlk70000023_02_msg0005
rows.name:
Ornella-sama was not just strong, she
was kind. And exceptionally beautiful,
so they said.
